high_descs: Move to the island between the two chairs.
Pick up the white plate from the island.
Bring the plate to the fridge.
Chill the plate in the fridge for a few seconds.
Bring the plate to the sink.
Put the plate down on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled plate down on the counter to the left of the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the door then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the white plate from in front of the book.
Turn right and walk around the counter to the left until you reach the fridge.
Cool the plate in the fridge, then take it out.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the plate down on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold plate on the counter next to the sink.

high_descs: turn right and walk over to the kitchen island
grab a white plate off of the kitchen island
walk to the other side of the kitchen island and stand in front of the fridge
place the plate inside of the fridge, let it cool then take it out
turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink on the right
place the plate on the counter to the left of the kitchen sink
anns.task_desc: place a cooled plate to the left of the kitchen sink
